<span class="header1">Public Service paired with Social/Helping (GI)</span>

<p>Your high scores in "G" and "I" show that you are headed for a rewarding career.  You will be highly valued in the work force.  You also have the potential to make a real difference in the world.  You are a responsible, independent worker and you know how to make things happen.</p>
<p>Most occupations in this pairing require at least a Bachelor's Degree.  It is helpful to have a Master's Degree or Ph.D. if you hope to work in some of these occupations.</p>

